WEBVTT

00:04.040 --> 00:06.520
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: I have to earn my position.</font>

00:06.560 --> 00:09.120
<font color="#00ff00">ANSON: Sir Robert Peel</font>
<font color="#00ff00">will be Prime Minister one day.</font>

00:09.160 --> 00:12.800
<font color="#00ffff">HARRIET: You're not in danger</font>
<font color="#00ffff">from a harmless flirtation</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with a married woman.</font>

00:12.840 --> 00:15.440
<font color="#00ff00">I wanted to tell you I will be going</font>
<font color="#00ff00">back to Coburg shortly.</font>

00:15.480 --> 00:19.240
<font color="#00ffff">I find myself thinking about you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">when I'm at my sugar work.</font>

00:19.280 --> 00:22.400
<font color="#00ff00">I must congratulate you, sir.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">That was a fine speech.</font>

00:22.440 --> 00:26.360
<font color="#ffff00">The only way to avoid...conception</font>
<font color="#ffff00">is...abstinence.</font>

00:26.400 --> 00:29.720
# Gloriana

00:32.759 --> 00:38.360
