01:46.960 --> 01:48.960
Georg Friedrich Handel.

01:54.160 --> 01:56.160
German.

01:57.400 --> 01:58.520
(CLEARS THROAT)

02:02.360 --> 02:04.040
(MUSIC STOPS)

02:09.039 --> 02:11.039
<font color="#ffff00">Are you all right?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">It's nothing.</font>

02:18.600 --> 02:21.040
I am bilious. Quickly!

02:24.600 --> 02:27.720
<font color="#00ff00">Her Majesty is quite the little</font>
<font color="#00ff00">jack-in-the-box.</font>

02:27.760 --> 02:31.160
<font color="#00ffff">Women are queer cattle.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

02:31.200 --> 02:33.360
<font color="#ffff00">Of what do you gentlemen speak?</font>

02:33.400 --> 02:38.440
The music, sir.
It is very...well-constructed.

02:47.040 --> 02:49.040
(MURMURING)

03:02.200 --> 03:04.200
(MUSIC RESUMES)

03:10.040 --> 03:11.680
I felt unwell.

03:12.960 --> 03:16.240
It was disagreeable. It's over now.

03:16.280 --> 03:18.280
(GROANS) Oh, Lord.

03:18.320 --> 03:20.640
It was nothing compared
to the spectacle

03:20.680 --> 03:24.600
of Peel perspiring with the effort
of being charming.

03:24.640 --> 03:28.160
<font color="#ffff00">Although I have to admit,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I'm strangely drawn to Peel.</font>

03:29.160 --> 03:33.720
<font color="#ffff00">He's...direct. Like me.</font>

03:33.760 --> 03:37.040
<font color="#ffff00">And also, I'm told he's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">an aficionado of the railway.</font>

03:38.400 --> 03:40.080
Don't talk railway at me.

03:40.120 --> 03:41.760
Half the people in this box

03:41.800 --> 03:44.280
are moaning about incursions
on their property.

03:44.960 --> 03:46.200
<font color="#ffff00">They are wrong.</font>

03:46.960 --> 03:50.640
<font color="#ffff00">We stand on the brink of a modern</font>
<font color="#ffff00">revolution, Victoria.</font>

03:50.680 --> 03:52.720
<font color="#ffff00">Of science. Embrace it.</font>

03:52.760 --> 03:55.000
<font color="#ffff00">Go to these places</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of new manufacturing.</font>

03:55.040 --> 03:58.640
You say manufacturing
and my soul shrivels with boredom.

03:58.680 --> 04:00.680
<font color="#ffff00">Mine does not.</font>

04:03.240 --> 04:06.680
<font color="#ffff00">You should be the champion</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of what is coming.</font>

04:06.720 --> 04:08.360
Rather too much "should".

04:08.400 --> 04:10.040
<font color="#ffff00">You're tired.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not tired.</font>

04:10.080 --> 04:13.240
<font color="#ffff00">Then, my dear...you must be ill.</font>

04:13.280 --> 04:15.280
I'm not ill.

04:15.320 --> 04:17.320
<font color="#ffff00">I shall send for the doctor.</font>

04:17.360 --> 04:20.560
Albert, I don't...
I don't want a doctor.

04:20.600 --> 04:22.600
<font color="#00ff00">Your Queen is sick.</font>

04:22.640 --> 04:25.520
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, we don't say "sick".</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We say "indisposed".</font>

04:26.480 --> 04:30.720
<font color="#00ff00">Well, she is "indisposed"</font>
<font color="#00ff00">out of her mouth.</font>

04:35.800 --> 04:37.800
<font color="#00ffff">What's that?</font>

04:37.840 --> 04:41.480
<font color="#ffff00">The cure for every ailment</font>
<font color="#ffff00">known to woman...</font>

04:42.760 --> 04:45.480
<font color="#ffff00">..chocolat.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Hot chocolate? Really?</font>

04:46.680 --> 04:48.680
<font color="#ffff00">Ah, ah, ah...</font>

04:53.800 --> 04:55.800
<font color="#00ffff">Mm!</font>

04:56.800 --> 04:59.800
<font color="#00ffff">Why don't you give her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">one of your little wafers to dip in?</font>

05:05.280 --> 05:06.880
(CRUNCHING)

05:08.560 --> 05:10.400
<font color="#ffff00">You're in the wrong job,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Miss Skerrett.</font>

05:11.080 --> 05:14.160
<font color="#00ffff">Thank you. I'll get this to the</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Queen directly.</font>

05:17.520 --> 05:20.120
<font color="#00ff00">Can't fix what she's got</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with chocolate.</font>

05:21.680 --> 05:25.080
<font color="#ffff00">She says, "No doctor",</font>
<font color="#ffff00">then she sends for the doctor...</font>

05:28.560 --> 05:29.960
MAN: Goodbye, Doctor Clark.

05:31.560 --> 05:33.560
<font color="#ffff00">What did the doctor say?</font>

05:36.080 --> 05:38.560
<font color="#ffff00">Tell me, please. There's nothing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">we cannot face.</font>

05:41.040 --> 05:43.040
(SNIFFS)

05:43.080 --> 05:46.920
There is no...polite English word.

05:46.960 --> 05:49.000
<font color="#ffff00">You are with child?</font>

05:50.560 --> 05:52.560
<font color="#ffff00">That's...</font>

05:53.160 --> 05:54.760
<font color="#ffff00">That's magnificent.</font>

05:54.800 --> 05:56.520
<font color="#ffff00">You are magnificent.</font>

05:58.840 --> 06:00.840
I'm afraid.

06:00.880 --> 06:02.880
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

06:18.440 --> 06:19.960
<font color="#ffff00">Is it safe to announce?</font>

06:20.000 --> 06:22.000
(APPLAUSE)

06:31.800 --> 06:34.520
<font color="#00ff00">I know my duty.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Very good, Lord Chamberlain.</font>

06:39.320 --> 06:41.480
<font color="#ffff00">HRH didn't dilly-dally.</font>

06:41.520 --> 06:43.360
(APPLAUSE CONTINUES)

06:55.560 --> 06:57.560
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am.</font>

07:00.360 --> 07:03.320
<font color="#ffff00">What is it?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Brandy mixed with cream.</font>

07:03.360 --> 07:05.360
<font color="#00ff00">It eliminates nausea.</font>

07:07.640 --> 07:09.080
<font color="#ffff00">Is it medically demonstrable?</font>

07:09.120 --> 07:11.200
<font color="#00ff00">Ask any woman</font>
<font color="#00ff00">who has conceived.</font>

07:17.880 --> 07:20.880
<font color="#00ff00">Listen to me.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your nurse is a virgin,</font>

07:20.920 --> 07:23.320
<font color="#00ff00">your husband is a man,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">your doctor is a fool.</font>

07:23.360 --> 07:26.200
<font color="#00ff00">Directly after luncheon</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you must go to bed,</font>

07:26.240 --> 07:28.560
<font color="#00ff00">lay down on your back</font>
<font color="#00ff00">without moving till dinner.</font>

07:28.600 --> 07:31.720
<font color="#00ff00">Dinner shall be preparations</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of the vital organs.</font>

07:31.760 --> 07:34.080
<font color="#00ff00">The brain, liver, the lungs.</font>

07:34.120 --> 07:36.120
Affairs of state...

07:36.160 --> 07:38.720
<font color="#00ff00">Drina, this is your affair of state.</font>

07:38.760 --> 07:40.920
<font color="#00ff00">Affairs? Let Albert do them for you.</font>

07:40.960 --> 07:42.840
<font color="#00ff00">Let him do everything for you.</font>

07:43.960 --> 07:45.960
Will he also give birth for me, Mama?

07:46.000 --> 07:48.000
<font color="#00ff00">Remember Charlotte.</font>

07:48.040 --> 07:50.600
<font color="#00ff00">Her death in labour</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is the reason you're Queen.</font>

07:54.840 --> 07:56.240
I've work to do.

08:05.080 --> 08:07.800
<font color="#ffff00">Baroness, you put me off my stroke.</font>

08:07.840 --> 08:11.080
<font color="#ffff00">The Queen must have sweetbreads</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in broth.</font>

08:11.120 --> 08:13.440
<font color="#ffff00">I know, yes, I'll see to it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">directly,</font>

08:13.480 --> 08:15.040
<font color="#ffff00">but if I cock this mayonnaise...</font>

08:15.080 --> 08:17.640
<font color="#00ffff">Her Majesty's dietary requirements</font>
<font color="#00ffff">take...</font>

08:19.160 --> 08:21.160
<font color="#ffff00">Curdled!</font>

08:28.160 --> 08:30.480
All she had to do was look at it.

08:32.360 --> 08:34.000
<font color="#ffff00">Take this.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Make it again.</font>

08:34.039 --> 08:36.039
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

08:40.960 --> 08:42.679
I'm not an imbecile.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.920
I grasp that the constitution
demands an heir

08:44.960 --> 08:46.960
and that I must produce it, but...

08:47.000 --> 08:49.520
to make me feel
I own no other function...

08:49.560 --> 08:51.560
<font color="#ffff00">Your mother is er...</font>

08:53.240 --> 08:55.240
<font color="#ffff00">..of her generation.</font>

08:55.280 --> 08:58.320
<font color="#ffff00">The world is leaving her behind.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">She's afraid.</font>

09:01.680 --> 09:05.160
You are going to look at my body
and be revolted. I...

09:06.320 --> 09:08.360
I know it.

09:08.400 --> 09:10.400
<font color="#ffff00">My desire for you will never fail.</font>

09:13.520 --> 09:16.360
<font color="#ffff00">A love like ours</font>
<font color="#ffff00">can burn down a city.</font>

09:20.960 --> 09:22.960
(DOOR OPENS)

09:23.000 --> 09:26.120
<font color="#00ffff">The Lord Chamberlain,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Your Majesty.</font>

09:40.680 --> 09:43.920
My Lord. This is my private time.

09:45.720 --> 09:47.160
Speak freely before the Prince.

09:47.200 --> 09:49.400
I shall be offended if you don't.

09:49.440 --> 09:52.960
<font color="#00ff00">The court rejoices in your news.</font>

09:53.000 --> 09:55.440
But? Your eyes are full of "but".

09:55.480 --> 09:59.640
<font color="#00ff00">Childbirth is a hazardous business.</font>

09:59.680 --> 10:02.040
You want to know
what will happen if I die.

10:02.080 --> 10:04.080
I understand.

10:04.120 --> 10:06.440
It is your duty to consider
what would happen next.

10:06.480 --> 10:09.640
<font color="#00ff00">Specifically, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">if the child survived you.</font>

10:11.240 --> 10:13.000
<font color="#00ff00">It is incumbent upon Your Majesty</font>

10:13.040 --> 10:14.600
<font color="#00ff00">to nominate a Regent</font>

10:14.640 --> 10:16.640
<font color="#00ff00">for the approval of Parliament.</font>

10:16.680 --> 10:20.360
Well, that, my Lord, is something I
can do without a moment's hesitation.

10:22.840 --> 10:26.120
<font color="#00ffff">And so the torpid Teuton</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wedges himself yet further</font>

10:26.160 --> 10:28.880
<font color="#00ffff">into the sagging cleft of power!</font>

10:28.920 --> 10:31.120
<font color="#00ffff">It's unconscionable!</font>

10:31.160 --> 10:35.560
<font color="#00ffff">If the Queen dies,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">are we to be ruled by a German?</font>

10:35.600 --> 10:37.600
<font color="#ffff00">We already are.</font>

10:37.640 --> 10:42.440
<font color="#00ffff">Cumberland would crawl over broken</font>
<font color="#00ffff">glass for a crack at the Regency.</font>

10:42.480 --> 10:44.320
<font color="#ffff00">Parliament, of course, must ratify.</font>

10:44.360 --> 10:45.880
Of course it must.

10:45.920 --> 10:49.520
<font color="#00ffff">I hear you are already acquainted</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the Prince, Peel.</font>

10:49.560 --> 10:51.320
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen is stubborn.</font>

10:51.360 --> 10:54.760
<font color="#00ffff">You must convince Albert</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to reconsider.</font>

10:56.480 --> 10:58.560
If the Tories fail
to condone your Regency...

10:59.560 --> 11:01.560
..I will abdicate.

11:01.600 --> 11:03.120
<font color="#ffff00">No, you will not.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I will.</font>

11:03.160 --> 11:05.400
You can't abdicate.
You're not the monarch.

11:05.440 --> 11:07.160
<font color="#ffff00">Then I will merely leave.</font>

11:07.200 --> 11:09.200
Then I will merely kill myself.

11:10.200 --> 11:13.000
<font color="#ffff00">Then I will remarry.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(LAUGHS) Ridiculous!</font>

11:13.040 --> 11:15.040
Who will you marry?

11:15.080 --> 11:17.280
<font color="#ffff00">Wellington? Peel? Maybe both.</font>

11:17.320 --> 11:18.440
(DOOR OPENS)

11:18.480 --> 11:21.000
<font color="#ffff00">Cumberland shall be my mistress.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(LAUGHS)</font>

11:21.040 --> 11:23.560
<font color="#00ff00">Drina... Laughter is bad for baby.</font>

11:29.840 --> 11:34.600
One day, I'll put her on a donkey
and pack her off to Carlisle.

11:34.640 --> 11:36.160
(DOOR CLOSES)
<font color="#ffff00">Carlisle?</font>

11:36.200 --> 11:38.200
<font color="#ffff00">County town of Cumberland.</font>

11:38.240 --> 11:41.560
<font color="#ffff00">Celebrated for textiles.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Adjacent is Northumberland,</font>

11:41.600 --> 11:43.200
<font color="#ffff00">rejoicing in the digging of coal.</font>

11:44.440 --> 11:47.640
<font color="#ffff00">You see, it is not your mother</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you should be sending north.</font>

11:48.400 --> 11:52.880
You're determined to see me dragged
around some morbid display
of traction engines.

11:52.920 --> 11:55.040
<font color="#ffff00">Send me.</font>

11:56.680 --> 11:57.800
Why?

11:57.840 --> 12:00.640
<font color="#ffff00">Otherwise I feel the people</font>
<font color="#ffff00">may not accept me as their Regent.</font>

12:03.160 --> 12:05.160
I'm not dead yet.

12:05.200 --> 12:07.000
<font color="#ffff00">Don't be childish.</font>

12:07.040 --> 12:09.440
If you would prefer not to be Regent
when I am dead...

12:09.480 --> 12:12.000
<font color="#ffff00">No, what I would prefer, Victoria,</font>

12:12.040 --> 12:17.080
<font color="#ffff00">is to exercise just a little power</font>
<font color="#ffff00">while you are alive.</font>

12:19.880 --> 12:21.880
Power must be seen to come from me.

12:28.600 --> 12:32.960
For you...I order a trip north.

12:34.000 --> 12:36.920
An expedition into the dark heart
of the Tory Shires

12:36.960 --> 12:40.040
where I shall fanfare you as Regent.

12:40.080 --> 12:42.760
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, no. I do not seriously expect</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you to travel.</font>

12:42.800 --> 12:44.360
<font color="#ffff00">The latest research in Germany</font>

12:44.400 --> 12:47.200
<font color="#ffff00">suggests a woman in pregnancy</font>
<font color="#ffff00">should not exert herself.</font>

12:47.240 --> 12:48.920
But I am not a German woman.

12:48.960 --> 12:50.960
I am the Queen of England.

13:01.440 --> 13:05.400
<font color="#00ffff">Chillington Hall, ma'am, is well</font>
<font color="#00ffff">situated for your research,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">being in Staffordshire.</font>

13:05.440 --> 13:07.120
<font color="#00ffff">It is also close to Drayton,</font>

13:07.160 --> 13:09.160
<font color="#00ffff">Sir Robert Peel's residence.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, Lord.</font>

13:09.200 --> 13:11.320
<font color="#00ffff">Your host, Sir Piers Giffard,</font>

13:11.360 --> 13:13.880
<font color="#00ffff">is, by all accounts,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">an old-fashioned gentleman</font>

13:13.920 --> 13:15.560
<font color="#00ffff">and a Tory as well.</font>

13:15.600 --> 13:18.600
<font color="#00ffff">But he begs to receive Her Majesty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and her entourage.</font>

13:18.640 --> 13:21.800
Contrary to general belief, I'm not
actually frightened of Tories.

13:22.480 --> 13:24.440
Can we define "entourage"?

13:24.480 --> 13:26.840
<font color="#00ffff">King Charles I, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">made such excursions</font>

13:26.880 --> 13:29.160
<font color="#00ffff">with what he called</font>
<font color="#00ffff">his "modest night bag".</font>

13:29.200 --> 13:31.400
<font color="#00ffff">A company of 500 horse.</font>

13:31.440 --> 13:33.440
Not an easy guest!

13:33.480 --> 13:36.160
One is anxious not to end one's reign
as did King Charles.

13:36.960 --> 13:39.160
We shall be attended by a very few.

13:39.200 --> 13:41.960
Jenkins. Your Royal Highness?

13:42.000 --> 13:45.960
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, erm, Lohlein is all I require.</font>

13:46.000 --> 13:48.040
Baroness, you, of course.

13:48.080 --> 13:49.920
Can't travel without my dear Lehzen.

13:49.960 --> 13:53.760
<font color="#ffff00">Surely, dear, Baroness is needed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">here to administrate...</font>

13:53.800 --> 13:56.680
Penge can administrate the household.
It's what he's for.

13:57.160 --> 14:00.000
<font color="#00ff00">We shall be so light,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we shall travel like the wind.</font>

14:00.040 --> 14:01.640
No, Mama. You shall remain here.

14:06.080 --> 14:10.440
Harriet, you attend to the Duchess
in my absence.

14:10.480 --> 14:12.480
Can your husband spare you?

14:12.520 --> 14:14.920
<font color="#00ffff">He will not notice I'm gone, ma'am.</font>

14:22.600 --> 14:26.080
<font color="#ffff00">This, apparently, is the very</font>
<font color="#ffff00">discomfort the railway eliminates.</font>

14:26.120 --> 14:29.160
<font color="#ffff00">The vehicle runs on wheels</font>
<font color="#ffff00">which have...flanges,</font>

14:29.200 --> 14:31.480
<font color="#ffff00">I learnt this word,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">which fit precisely</font>

14:31.520 --> 14:33.960
<font color="#ffff00">into the inner tracks...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I think we need to stop.</font>

14:35.080 --> 14:37.080
Please, stay here.

14:40.240 --> 14:41.960
Why do you grab me with that, Lehzen?

14:42.000 --> 14:44.000
It doesn't appear to be raining.

14:44.040 --> 14:48.240
<font color="#00ffff">It was...in case Your Majesty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">was indisposed.</font>

14:48.280 --> 14:50.800
Oh, dearest Lehzen.

14:52.320 --> 14:55.160
Always thinking of me.
I just needed some air.

14:56.480 --> 15:00.240
You know, the whole world would have
me trussed up in bed all day.

15:01.640 --> 15:03.640
It's hardly my style, is it?

15:05.640 --> 15:08.360
(LAUGHS) What was it you used to say
I was?

15:10.760 --> 15:12.960
<font color="#00ffff">A little wrigglepants, ma'am.</font>

15:13.000 --> 15:14.720
(LAUGHS)

15:15.560 --> 15:16.840
(HORSES NEIGHING)

15:31.000 --> 15:33.200
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: Did you see those fellows</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in the field?</font>

15:33.240 --> 15:36.200
<font color="#ffff00">They were surveying</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the railway, I think.</font>

15:36.240 --> 15:40.480
VICTORIA: My darling, railway
is not a subject to be paraded
before the Giffards.

15:48.520 --> 15:52.080
Just be your charming self.
They will adore you.

15:55.000 --> 15:58.560
<font color="#00ffff">Last time I saw her</font>
<font color="#00ffff">she was, what, this high?</font>

15:59.560 --> 16:02.360
<font color="#00ff00">Apparently she still is.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

16:02.400 --> 16:04.400
<font color="#00ff00">She's here to pimp for his Regency.</font>

16:04.440 --> 16:06.280
<font color="#00ff00">Are you randy for it?</font>

16:06.320 --> 16:08.880
<font color="#00ffff">Not at any price.</font>

16:13.480 --> 16:17.080
<font color="#00ffff">Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Sir Piers.</font>

16:36.360 --> 16:39.000
So how does one pass one's time
in Staffordshire?

16:39.040 --> 16:43.560
<font color="#ffff00">Ceramics. It is the industry</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the region.</font>

16:43.600 --> 16:48.880
<font color="#00ffff">It is a-a-a favoured occupation</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of the people.</font>

16:48.920 --> 16:51.760
<font color="#ffff00">Well, it seems to be the case</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that many artefacts</font>

16:51.800 --> 16:56.080
<font color="#ffff00">are created en masse</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in the factories.</font>

16:57.360 --> 17:00.160
<font color="#ffff00">I would very much like to visit</font>
<font color="#ffff00">some of these places.</font>

17:02.000 --> 17:03.800
<font color="#00ffff">We hunt, ma'am.</font>

17:03.840 --> 17:07.760
<font color="#00ffff">In fact, I've arranged for you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and the Prince to ride out</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the Shifnal tomorrow.</font>

17:07.800 --> 17:10.079
<font color="#00ff00">Piers, you're quite mad.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Her Majesty cannot tax herself</font>

17:10.119 --> 17:12.560
<font color="#00ff00">to ride with the hounds</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in her condition.</font>

17:12.599 --> 17:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">Alas, I do not hunt.</font>

17:20.040 --> 17:22.040
<font color="#ffff00">I shoot.</font>

17:22.079 --> 17:24.640
<font color="#00ffff">A day of driven shooting, then.</font>

17:24.680 --> 17:27.079
<font color="#00ffff">Would Your Majesty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">find such a prospect diverting?</font>

17:27.119 --> 17:29.120
Excessively diverting.

17:29.160 --> 17:30.760
We shall observe, Lady Beatrice.

17:30.800 --> 17:34.040
I'm confident neither of us
shall find the experience taxing.

17:43.040 --> 17:46.400
<font color="#00ff00">Your man's shooting tomorrow.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Does he have the kit?</font>

17:46.440 --> 17:48.680
<font color="#00ff00">Hm. In this country,</font>

17:48.720 --> 17:52.760
<font color="#00ff00">a gentleman don't set foot in the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">field without the kit.</font>

17:54.880 --> 17:57.840
<font color="#00ff00">(SIGHS) Just see me afterwards.</font>

18:06.200 --> 18:07.560
<font color="#00ffff">Crikey, whose are those?</font>

18:07.600 --> 18:10.520
The butler gave these to me
for the Prince.

18:10.560 --> 18:12.360
Is correct English for the field.

18:12.400 --> 18:15.280
<font color="#00ffff">Those trousers aren't proper kit</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for nothing but fancy dress.</font>

18:15.320 --> 18:17.280
<font color="#00ffff">A gun wearing white</font>
<font color="#00ffff">would be a right howler.</font>

18:17.320 --> 18:19.880
<font color="#00ffff">Are you listening to me?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Are you listening? </font><font color="#ffffff"> Yes.</font>

18:19.920 --> 18:23.200
<font color="#00ffff">A dark coat. Brown boots. Tall hat.</font>

18:23.240 --> 18:25.200
<font color="#00ffff">The older the better.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">That's all you need.</font>

18:25.240 --> 18:29.200
<font color="#00ffff">No-one shoots in nothing new.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Do you understand?</font>

18:29.240 --> 18:31.560
Yes. <font color="#00ffff">Come on, show me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what you've brought.</font>

18:31.600 --> 18:33.320
<font color="#00ffff">I won't have the Prince embarrassed.</font>

18:34.320 --> 18:36.320
(DOGS BARKING)

18:39.720 --> 18:41.440
(YELLING)

18:41.480 --> 18:43.400
<font color="#ffff00">What are those gentlemen doing?</font>

18:43.440 --> 18:47.480
<font color="#00ffff">They're the beaters, sir. They're</font>
<font color="#00ffff">driving the birds towards us.</font>

18:47.520 --> 18:52.320
<font color="#ffff00">I see. In Thuringia, we take birds</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in cages to high towers.</font>

18:52.360 --> 18:54.240
<font color="#ffff00">And then they are released.</font>

18:54.280 --> 18:56.640
<font color="#00ffff">(QUIETLY) What a barbaric practice.</font>

18:56.680 --> 18:58.680
(BIRDS FLUTTERING)

19:02.200 --> 19:04.200
(BIRDS CAW)

19:10.040 --> 19:12.680
<font color="#00ffff">Sausage-eater can hit 'em!</font>
<font color="#00ff00">A most singular man.</font>

19:14.040 --> 19:16.040
<font color="#00ff00">Fascinating.</font>

19:20.360 --> 19:22.200
<font color="#ffff00">I "wipe your eye", Sir Piers.</font>

19:24.040 --> 19:26.040
<font color="#00ffff">Well shot, sir.</font>

19:32.280 --> 19:35.040
Oh. Extraordinary to find you here.

19:35.080 --> 19:39.680
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, extraordinary only in that I do</font>
<font color="#ffff00">not shoot, Your Majesty.</font>

19:39.720 --> 19:42.160
<font color="#ffff00">But I am neighbour to the Giffards.</font>

19:44.240 --> 19:45.560
You do not shoot?

19:45.600 --> 19:48.200
<font color="#ffff00">If you instruct me to do so, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I shall certainly try</font>

19:48.240 --> 19:50.920
<font color="#ffff00">but I am afraid I shall make</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a fearful hash of it.</font>

19:50.960 --> 19:55.360
<font color="#ffff00">Sport is not my metier.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I am unused to it.</font>

19:56.840 --> 19:58.920
Too busy preparing for government.

20:02.320 --> 20:04.320
Now, luncheon.

20:06.080 --> 20:08.200
<font color="#ffff00">Sir Piers, what is your view</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of the railway?</font>

20:08.560 --> 20:11.880
<font color="#00ffff">Fortunately, sir, I don't have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a view of it here.</font>

20:11.920 --> 20:14.880
<font color="#00ffff">I'm plagued by people wanting to run</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the thing through my park.</font>

20:14.920 --> 20:18.760
<font color="#00ffff">I tell them to cut along sharpish</font>
<font color="#00ffff">or I'll set the dogs on 'em.</font>

20:18.800 --> 20:20.800
<font color="#00ffff">He's a fan, mind.</font>

20:20.840 --> 20:23.640
<font color="#ffff00">You approve of it, Sir Robert?</font>

20:23.680 --> 20:26.440
<font color="#00ff00">One must not stand in the path</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of progress, sir.</font>

20:26.480 --> 20:31.760
<font color="#ffff00">I agree. I believe the railway</font>
<font color="#ffff00">dissolves the unnecessary cultural</font>
<font color="#ffff00">divides of our region.</font>

20:31.800 --> 20:34.680
<font color="#ffff00">Men can travel for work.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Families unite.</font>

20:34.720 --> 20:40.960
<font color="#00ffff">When you say..."our regions", sir,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">do you mean the counties of England?</font>

20:41.000 --> 20:45.560
<font color="#00ffff">Because you may find that the people</font>
<font color="#00ffff">of, for instance, Staffordshire,</font>

20:45.600 --> 20:49.720
<font color="#00ffff">are rather fond of the peculiar</font>
<font color="#00ffff">virtues of their region</font>

20:49.760 --> 20:54.800
<font color="#00ffff">and don't necessarily</font>
<font color="#00ffff">want it disfigured by iron rails.</font>

20:54.840 --> 20:57.160
As ever, this subject
makes men overstimulated.

20:57.200 --> 21:00.320
<font color="#00ff00">Am I right in thinking you have</font>
<font color="#00ff00">never seen a locomotive, sir?</font>

21:00.360 --> 21:01.640
<font color="#ffff00">That's correct.</font>

21:01.680 --> 21:04.960
<font color="#00ff00">Well, there is presently</font>
<font color="#00ff00">one on my property at Drayton.</font>

21:05.000 --> 21:06.600
<font color="#00ff00">It is quite adjacent.</font>

21:06.640 --> 21:09.640
<font color="#00ff00">It would be my pleasure</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to offer you all a demonstration.</font>

21:09.680 --> 21:12.880
<font color="#ffff00">Excellent. Excellent.</font>

21:12.920 --> 21:14.920
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria?</font>

21:14.960 --> 21:17.800
Alas, Sir Robert,
I think we should let our host

21:17.840 --> 21:20.120
devise the programme of activity.

21:20.160 --> 21:22.040
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty is pale.</font>

21:22.080 --> 21:24.720
<font color="#00ff00">It is too silly of us to expect</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you to remain at table.</font>

21:24.760 --> 21:26.880
<font color="#00ff00">So fatiguing...</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I am quite well, thank you.</font>

21:26.920 --> 21:28.680
<font color="#00ff00">..when baby is being mischievous.</font>

21:28.720 --> 21:30.560
<font color="#00ff00">Would you care to rest, ma'am?</font>

21:33.520 --> 21:35.520
I think I shall explore.

21:35.560 --> 21:37.560
Alone.

21:39.000 --> 21:41.000
(WHISPERS) You count as alone.

21:46.200 --> 21:48.160
To look up over one's stew

21:48.200 --> 21:50.640
and see Peel fidgeting
with the silver

21:50.680 --> 21:52.680
and simpering over my husband...

21:54.520 --> 21:59.040
Albert doesn't know how to talk.
He refuses to dissemble.

21:59.080 --> 22:00.840
He only ever says
exactly what he means

22:00.880 --> 22:03.160
and amongst people like the Giffards,
it's...

22:04.760 --> 22:06.880
..hopeless.

22:06.920 --> 22:08.320
Oh, say something, Lehzen.

22:08.360 --> 22:10.360
You're allowed to say something.

22:11.360 --> 22:14.040
<font color="#00ffff">Sir Robert reminds me of an exhibit</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I saw in Salzburg.</font>

22:15.640 --> 22:18.280
<font color="#00ffff">It was a big frog. Stuffed.</font>

22:22.440 --> 22:24.880
You accuse Sir Robert
of looking like a stuffed frog?

22:28.360 --> 22:30.360
(BOTH LAUGH)

22:32.960 --> 22:37.400
<font color="#00ffff">Now listen to me, Peel.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I know you've had disappointments</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in your life.</font>

22:37.440 --> 22:40.560
<font color="#00ffff">Harrow, so forth.</font>

22:40.600 --> 22:44.440
<font color="#00ffff">But the future belongs to the Tories</font>

22:44.480 --> 22:47.560
<font color="#00ffff">and the Tories belong to you.</font>

22:47.600 --> 22:49.600
<font color="#00ffff">Coast to the port, damn you.</font>

22:52.280 --> 22:54.240
<font color="#00ffff">So make yourself fit for us.</font>

22:55.240 --> 22:57.320
<font color="#ffff00">In what respect am I not fit?</font>

22:57.360 --> 22:58.800
<font color="#00ffff">You pander to the railway</font>

22:58.840 --> 23:01.360
<font color="#00ffff">when you should be chasing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the bastards off your land.</font>

23:01.400 --> 23:05.800
<font color="#00ffff">You poodlefake and pussyfoot</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about the gormless German.</font>

23:05.840 --> 23:09.760
<font color="#00ffff">It's perfectly clear</font>
<font color="#00ffff">why they've invited themselves here.</font>

23:09.800 --> 23:13.240
<font color="#00ffff">Only reason he talks to you is to</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ginger up support for his Regency.</font>

23:13.280 --> 23:16.760
<font color="#00ffff">An office you shall not allow him.</font>

23:17.400 --> 23:21.400
<font color="#00ffff">Wellington's not too old</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to take the reins, you know.</font>

23:25.280 --> 23:27.280
<font color="#00ffff">Just saying.</font>

23:30.680 --> 23:32.680
(CLOCK TICKS)

23:41.760 --> 23:44.040
You imagine I resent being left here
by the Queen.

23:45.200 --> 23:47.240
Well, you are correct.

23:48.440 --> 23:50.600
<font color="#00ffff">It's never nice</font>
<font color="#00ffff">being left behind, Duchess.</font>

24:11.360 --> 24:12.920
<font color="#00ff00">Did you make that just for me?</font>

24:12.960 --> 24:15.360
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you are now</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my official taster.</font>

24:21.280 --> 24:23.840
<font color="#00ff00">That's extraordinary. (LAUGHS)</font>

24:24.920 --> 24:26.920
<font color="#00ff00">You know what would make that</font>
<font color="#00ff00">even better?</font>

24:26.960 --> 24:29.480
<font color="#ffff00">Here we go.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Cover it in hot chocolate.</font>

24:31.480 --> 24:33.840
<font color="#ffff00">I think, Miss Skerrett,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you might be a genius.</font>

24:33.880 --> 24:35.880
<font color="#00ff00">(LAUGHS)</font>

24:41.720 --> 24:43.720
Forgive me, darling, but...

24:44.320 --> 24:46.600
..sometimes you're too direct
when you speak.

24:47.200 --> 24:50.280
Men like Giffard,
they recoil from enthusiasm.

24:51.800 --> 24:53.800
They find it un-English.

24:55.560 --> 24:59.600
Please, from now on,
let me guide the conversation.

24:59.640 --> 25:02.320
I'm sorry about the locomotive.

25:03.480 --> 25:05.480
But we must proceed carefully.

25:13.640 --> 25:16.600
<font color="#00ff00">(SPEAKS IN GERMAN)</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Speak English.</font>

25:17.760 --> 25:20.040
<font color="#ffff00">I have this morning sent a note</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to Sir Robert Peel.</font>

25:20.080 --> 25:23.480
<font color="#ffff00">Today, I see the locomotive.</font>

25:30.880 --> 25:32.880
Albert?

25:46.160 --> 25:49.840
<font color="#ffff00">That is the most magnificent thing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">I have ever seen.</font>

25:53.960 --> 25:55.760
(HORSE WHINNIES)

25:55.800 --> 25:57.680
(PUMPING)

26:00.680 --> 26:02.560
(STEAM HISSES)

26:03.760 --> 26:05.680
<font color="#ffff00">Good day.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your Highness.</font>

26:06.760 --> 26:10.200
Morning. Would you show His Royal
Highness the controls, please?

26:11.160 --> 26:13.040
<font color="#00ff00">These levers control the valves.</font>

26:14.480 --> 26:16.640
<font color="#00ff00">Pedal engages the eccentrics.</font>

26:16.680 --> 26:18.720
<font color="#00ff00">Regulator controls the motion.</font>

26:18.760 --> 26:20.760
<font color="#ffff00">Moderates the flow of steam.</font>

26:25.320 --> 26:27.320
<font color="#00ff00">Let's go.</font>

26:27.360 --> 26:30.720
<font color="#00ff00">Now, please, Your Worships,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you can take a seat in the carriage.</font>

26:30.760 --> 26:33.960
<font color="#ffff00">Carriage be damned. We ride here.</font>

26:37.800 --> 26:38.920
(HISSING)

26:39.000 --> 26:41.440
(WHISTLE)

26:41.480 --> 26:44.400
(STEAM HISSES, ENGINE PUFFS)

27:01.080 --> 27:03.160
I said I wished to be alone.

27:06.040 --> 27:08.040
<font color="#00ffff">Shall I go, Majesty?</font>

27:08.080 --> 27:09.400
No.

27:11.000 --> 27:13.080
<font color="#00ffff">You haven't eaten your beetroot,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">ma'am.</font>

27:19.320 --> 27:23.240
I can't bear this. Where is he?

27:33.000 --> 27:35.000
(WHISTLE)

27:40.400 --> 27:42.400
<font color="#ffff00">This is the future!</font>

27:42.440 --> 27:45.040
Yes, sir.
(WHISTLE)

27:58.280 --> 28:00.280
<font color="#ffff00">How is the Queen?</font>

28:02.680 --> 28:05.360
<font color="#00ffff">Wanting the most peculiar things</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for breakfast.</font>

28:05.400 --> 28:08.640
<font color="#00ffff">This morning she had to have</font>
<font color="#00ffff">beetroot, a vegetable.</font>

28:08.680 --> 28:10.440
<font color="#00ffff">It's revolting.</font>

28:11.280 --> 28:14.160
<font color="#00ffff">She's rather cross that HRH</font>
<font color="#00ffff">has gone off somewhere without her.</font>

28:14.200 --> 28:16.200
<font color="#ffff00">Also without me, but...</font>

28:16.240 --> 28:21.200
<font color="#ffff00">..for a man, it is essential</font>
<font color="#ffff00">to have space. To breathe.</font>

28:22.640 --> 28:25.640
<font color="#00ffff">It's not only men who need a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">breather from matrimony, my dear.</font>

28:27.680 --> 28:31.560
<font color="#ffff00">Er, the butler said</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that in the country</font>

28:31.600 --> 28:34.600
<font color="#ffff00">the Prince must sing</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as he's being undressed.</font>

28:34.640 --> 28:36.920
<font color="#ffff00">I am to encourage this.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Sing?</font>

28:36.960 --> 28:38.960
<font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Anything in particular?</font>

28:39.000 --> 28:41.160
<font color="#ffff00">God Save The Queen.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Good heavens.</font>

28:41.280 --> 28:43.560
<font color="#00ffff">You've been had, boy.</font>

28:43.600 --> 28:45.680
<font color="#00ffff">This butler wants your master</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to look a fool.</font>

28:47.400 --> 28:50.400
<font color="#ffff00">Why? </font><font color="#00ffff"> Because these people</font>
<font color="#00ffff">like the Giffards</font>

28:50.440 --> 28:52.440
<font color="#00ffff">and their servants,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">they're all the same.</font>

28:52.480 --> 28:55.880
<font color="#00ffff">Got to keep the old ways.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Anything that is young and new</font>
<font color="#00ffff">is a threat.</font>

28:55.920 --> 29:00.040
<font color="#00ffff">The Queen, the Prince, you.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">You're what's next.</font>

29:00.080 --> 29:02.080
<font color="#00ffff">You scare them.</font>

29:07.560 --> 29:10.640
I'm going for a walk.
<font color="#00ff00">Without the Prince?</font>

29:13.880 --> 29:15.880
Sir Piers.

29:15.920 --> 29:17.200
<font color="#00ff00">Ma'am?</font>

29:17.240 --> 29:19.520
As we are presently unencumbered
by other guests,

29:19.560 --> 29:22.040
may I ask where you stand
on the matter of the Regency?

29:22.080 --> 29:27.600
<font color="#00ff00">This is surely a matter, ma'am,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that is purely hypothetical?</font>

29:27.640 --> 29:29.440
Parliament is not hypothetical.

29:29.480 --> 29:32.240
Its members must condone
my selection.

29:32.280 --> 29:34.280
Condone or condemn.

29:35.960 --> 29:37.960
What would you advise them to do?

29:39.560 --> 29:43.760
<font color="#00ff00">What all men of honour must do,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">ma'am.</font>

29:43.800 --> 29:46.040
<font color="#00ff00">Follow their consciences.</font>

29:50.600 --> 29:51.880
(QUIETLY) Weasel.

29:53.000 --> 29:54.360
(WHISTLE)

29:55.320 --> 29:57.280
<font color="#ffff00">Sir Robert, do you consort with me</font>

29:57.320 --> 29:59.960
<font color="#ffff00">because you seek my favour</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for your political advantage?</font>

30:00.000 --> 30:03.520
No, sir. Do you consort with me

30:03.560 --> 30:06.720
because you seek my influence
to ratify your Regency?

30:06.760 --> 30:09.080
<font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

30:09.120 --> 30:11.880
<font color="#ffff00">Although that would be rather</font>
<font color="#ffff00">helpful. Perhaps I should.</font>

30:13.160 --> 30:15.200
<font color="#ffff00">I like you, Sir Robert.</font>

30:15.240 --> 30:19.200
<font color="#ffff00">You know I famously have no taste,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of course. I'm German.</font>

30:19.240 --> 30:21.520
(LAUGHS)
<font color="#ffff00">There it is.</font>

30:23.560 --> 30:25.080
I am glad of it, sir.

30:28.240 --> 30:29.960
<font color="#ffff00">There it is.</font>

30:31.240 --> 30:34.280
(WHISTLE)

30:40.720 --> 30:42.720
<font color="#00ff00">Does your hand contain royalty?</font>

30:44.680 --> 30:46.680
<font color="#00ffff">As a matter of fact, it does.</font>

30:46.720 --> 30:48.680
<font color="#00ff00">A prince?</font>

30:50.280 --> 30:53.200
<font color="#00ff00">Of course, I mean knave.</font>

30:56.840 --> 30:59.120
<font color="#00ff00">Ernest is not an honest man,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Harriet.</font>

30:59.160 --> 31:01.160
<font color="#00ffff">I'm a married woman, Duchess.</font>

31:02.160 --> 31:04.160
<font color="#00ff00">You've got children.</font>

31:06.080 --> 31:08.000
<font color="#00ff00">As I had Victoria.</font>

31:15.240 --> 31:17.240
(HORSE AND CARRIAGE APPROACHING)

31:27.200 --> 31:28.960
(INAUDIBLE CHATTER)

31:37.640 --> 31:39.640
How dare you.

31:39.680 --> 31:41.200
<font color="#ffff00">My dear, I did not want to wake you.</font>

31:44.240 --> 31:46.480
It is such an insult.

31:46.520 --> 31:48.280
<font color="#ffff00">It's not an insult, Victoria.</font>

31:49.360 --> 31:53.600
<font color="#ffff00">It was merely me embracing England's</font>
<font color="#ffff00">destiny on your behalf.</font>

31:53.640 --> 31:56.200
It is not your place
to do things on my behalf!

31:56.240 --> 31:59.920
If I wish to bring railways,
or anything, to the attention
of the English people,

31:59.960 --> 32:01.640
then, Albert, I shall do it myself!

32:01.680 --> 32:05.880
And if you answer back using the word
"future", I shall scream!

32:06.880 --> 32:09.440
I decide what is the future.

32:11.440 --> 32:12.800
What if you had been killed?

32:12.840 --> 32:14.920
Do you not care at all
about our unborn child?

32:16.920 --> 32:19.520
Look at you. You look like a peasant.

32:19.560 --> 32:21.560
<font color="#ffff00">I'm not the one eating beetroot.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">What?</font>

32:21.600 --> 32:24.000
What is wrong with beetroot?
<font color="#ffff00">It's peasant food.</font>

32:24.040 --> 32:26.840
That is ridiculous! Possibly in your
country, not in mine...

32:26.880 --> 32:28.880
<font color="#ffff00">This is my country!</font>

32:30.480 --> 32:33.440
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria, I seek only to serve it.</font>

32:35.920 --> 32:37.920
<font color="#ffff00">And yourself.</font>

33:17.920 --> 33:21.240
<font color="#00ff00">(CLEARS THROAT) Dining with the</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Queen, Mr Francatelli?</font>

33:58.840 --> 34:00.680
<font color="#ffff00">Where's the Queen?</font>

34:00.720 --> 34:04.480
<font color="#00ff00">She didn't shed a rod,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">her wheels didn't fall off...</font>

34:06.520 --> 34:08.520
<font color="#00ff00">..and she didn't kill Prince Albert.</font>

34:10.120 --> 34:13.199
<font color="#00ff00">I call it a success.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Your blooming good health, boys.</font>

34:13.239 --> 34:16.560
<font color="#ffff00">ALL: Good health.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(HORSE WHINNIES)</font>

34:27.199 --> 34:28.560
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, Christ.</font>

34:28.600 --> 34:30.639
(HISSING)

34:34.239 --> 34:36.239
(GEARS GRINDING)

34:40.480 --> 34:42.480
(WHISTLE)

35:03.120 --> 35:05.120
(WHISTLE)

35:07.680 --> 35:10.360
<font color="#ffff00">Victoria! Victoria!</font>

35:13.120 --> 35:14.960
<font color="#ffff00">You like it?</font>

35:16.800 --> 35:18.800
I love it!
<font color="#ffff00">What?</font>

35:18.840 --> 35:21.440
I said I love it!

35:26.720 --> 35:28.720
(WHISTLE)

36:00.000 --> 36:01.960
<font color="#ffff00">Now.</font>

36:04.720 --> 36:06.480
<font color="#00ffff">(GIGGLES)</font>

36:12.480 --> 36:13.920
(PINGS)
<font color="#00ffff">(LAUGHS)</font>

36:35.160 --> 36:36.960
<font color="#00ffff">It's wonderful.</font>

36:40.560 --> 36:42.640
<font color="#00ffff">You know what you ought to do?</font>

36:44.800 --> 36:49.240
<font color="#00ffff">Call it...a bomb surprise.</font>

36:49.280 --> 36:51.720
<font color="#00ffff">Because it looks like a bomb, yeah?</font>

36:51.760 --> 36:54.080
<font color="#00ffff">And it's a surprise!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">(BOTH LAUGH)</font>

37:00.080 --> 37:02.760
<font color="#ffff00">La bombe surprise.</font>

37:03.480 --> 37:08.160
<font color="#00ffff">Mr Francatelli's bombe surprise.</font>

37:08.200 --> 37:11.040
<font color="#00ffff">You invented it.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">No, you invented it.</font>

37:12.560 --> 37:14.400
<font color="#00ffff">We invented it.</font>

37:33.720 --> 37:37.280
<font color="#00ff00">It won't wash, Peel.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What won't, Sir Piers?</font>

37:37.320 --> 37:39.360
<font color="#00ff00">Licking up to the Queen's husband</font>

37:39.400 --> 37:42.920
<font color="#00ff00">and giving him a ride</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on your ruddy infernal machine.</font>

37:42.960 --> 37:46.680
<font color="#00ff00">It is not an adult way</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to solicit power.</font>

37:46.720 --> 37:50.120
<font color="#00ffff">The Prince has no power</font>
<font color="#00ffff">to be solicited.</font>

37:50.160 --> 37:52.160
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, you're wrong.</font>

37:53.160 --> 37:54.440
<font color="#ffff00">With respect.</font>

38:03.280 --> 38:06.800
You know, Sir Piers, I rather enjoyed
riding on the railway.

38:06.840 --> 38:08.600
I commend the experience to you.

38:10.040 --> 38:12.040
You might find it enlightening.

38:12.080 --> 38:16.160
<font color="#00ff00">I am most grateful</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for Your Majesty's advice.</font>

38:17.040 --> 38:20.920
It is a mistake to make one's mind up
about a thing before one's tried it.

38:21.600 --> 38:24.960
Don't you think?
The world is on the move, Sir Piers.

38:25.000 --> 38:27.000
Keep up.

38:27.040 --> 38:28.520
(FOOTMAN SHOUTS TO HORSES)

38:33.600 --> 38:34.760
(HORSE NEIGHS)

39:01.560 --> 39:03.560
(FOOTMAN SHOUTS TO HORSES)

39:07.560 --> 39:10.760
<font color="#ffff00">My darling. Whatever is the matter?</font>

39:15.520 --> 39:17.520
(SOBS)

39:17.560 --> 39:20.040
I am frightened of the pain.

39:23.520 --> 39:25.520
<font color="#ffff00">There will be pain, yes, but...</font>

39:27.800 --> 39:31.040
<font color="#ffff00">I wish I could endure it for you.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">But, Victoria, listen to me.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Listen...</font>

39:35.200 --> 39:36.680
<font color="#ffff00">You are strong.</font>

39:36.720 --> 39:40.920
<font color="#ffff00">Childbirth is surely an ordeal,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but you are equal to it.</font>

39:44.320 --> 39:49.400
<font color="#ffff00">You have such...such fortitude.</font>

39:53.720 --> 39:55.720
<font color="#ffff00">It was wrong of me.</font>

39:55.760 --> 39:57.760
(SNIFFS)

39:57.800 --> 40:02.320
<font color="#ffff00">Peel. The engine. To go alone.</font>

40:02.360 --> 40:04.640
No, not...not necessarily.

40:07.120 --> 40:09.760
<font color="#ffff00">You will allow me to share</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the burden of your duties?</font>

40:09.800 --> 40:11.800
Albert...

40:13.080 --> 40:14.880
..please.

40:14.920 --> 40:20.400
The Scots, you know, they...
they have a curious expression.

40:22.960 --> 40:26.680
"Softly, softly, catchee monkey."

40:28.800 --> 40:30.960
<font color="#ffff00">Who is this monkey?</font>

40:31.000 --> 40:33.000
You are my monkey.

40:39.400 --> 40:41.400
(BELLS CHIME)

40:45.720 --> 40:48.680
Did you see the Giffards
sniggering up their noses at me?

40:48.720 --> 40:50.560
<font color="#00ffff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

40:50.600 --> 40:51.880
<font color="#00ff00">My dear, you look so well.</font>

40:51.920 --> 40:53.920
Thank you, Mama.

40:55.360 --> 40:57.720
Expeditions clearly agree with us.

40:59.240 --> 41:01.320
I am afraid I didn't drink
your medicine.

41:01.360 --> 41:05.360
<font color="#00ff00">(CHUCKLES) The baby will tell you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">what it wants.</font>

41:10.880 --> 41:12.880
<font color="#00ff00">Welcome home.</font>

41:14.360 --> 41:18.880
(CLEARS THROAT)
Are we paying attention?

41:20.600 --> 41:25.440
The Queen has requested
a dish of bacon and peas.

41:25.480 --> 41:26.840
<font color="#00ffff">Is bacon suitable?</font>

41:26.880 --> 41:30.760
Medical suitability
has been suspended.

41:30.800 --> 41:33.520
Bacon, Mr Francatelli.
<font color="#ffff00">And peas, Mr Penge.</font>

41:33.560 --> 41:35.880
And peas.
<font color="#ffff00">Post-haste. And for the Prince?</font>

41:35.920 --> 41:38.720
The Prince dines with the Queen.

41:38.760 --> 41:40.760
<font color="#ffff00">Double bacon and peas!</font>

41:47.000 --> 41:50.400
<font color="#00ff00">It is Her Majesty's wish that her</font>
<font color="#00ff00">husband be Prince Regent</font>

41:50.440 --> 41:53.960
<font color="#00ff00">and I believe it is the correct</font>
<font color="#00ff00">choice. </font><font color="#ffffff"> (MURMURS)</font>

41:54.000 --> 41:58.080
<font color="#ffff00">You promote the costive Coburg</font>
<font color="#ffff00">as our Regent?</font>

41:58.120 --> 42:01.680
<font color="#00ff00">I do not promote the Prince.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">The man is a menace and a boor.</font>

42:01.720 --> 42:04.080
<font color="#00ff00">I endorse the decision of my Queen.</font>

42:04.120 --> 42:06.160
(JEERING)

42:06.200 --> 42:08.880
<font color="#00ff00">If you wish to make farmyard noises,</font>

42:08.920 --> 42:12.600
<font color="#00ff00">I suggest you cross the floor</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to Palmerston's sty</font>

42:12.640 --> 42:15.240
<font color="#00ff00">where that species of behaviour</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is tolerated.</font>

42:15.280 --> 42:18.240
<font color="#00ff00">This is the party of gentlemen.</font>

42:19.360 --> 42:21.360
<font color="#00ff00">Is that understood?</font>

42:22.680 --> 42:26.520
<font color="#00ff00">Let the Speaker be informed</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that the Tories wholeheartedly</font>

42:26.560 --> 42:29.240
<font color="#00ff00">support Her Majesty's choice</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of Regent.</font>

42:32.880 --> 42:34.880
<font color="#00ff00">There it is.</font>

42:40.040 --> 42:46.480
<font color="#ffff00">Well, if none of us has the moral</font>
<font color="#ffff00">courage to stand up to Peel,</font>

42:46.520 --> 42:49.640
<font color="#ffff00">I...I suggest we back him.</font>

42:51.840 --> 42:53.840
<font color="#ffff00">Is that understood?</font>

42:59.160 --> 43:00.640
(DOOR OPENS)

43:04.200 --> 43:06.200
<font color="#00ffff">(WHISPERS) The frog is here.</font>

43:06.240 --> 43:09.160
<font color="#00ffff">Wishing to croak at you.</font>

43:11.240 --> 43:12.680
<font color="#00ffff">I shall send him away.</font>

43:12.720 --> 43:14.720
No.

43:15.520 --> 43:18.160
Tell Sir Robert I shall be pleased
to see him.

43:31.640 --> 43:34.200
<font color="#00ff00">Your Majesty.</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Sir Robert.</font>

43:34.240 --> 43:37.000
You look rather more at home here
than you do in a muddy field.

43:37.040 --> 43:40.040
It's late. This must be important.

43:40.080 --> 43:42.080
<font color="#00ff00">It is indeed, ma'am.</font>

43:42.120 --> 43:46.760
<font color="#00ff00">I beg to inform Her Majesty that in</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the unfortunate event of her death,</font>

43:46.800 --> 43:50.480
<font color="#00ff00">her selection of Regent has</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the full support of the Tory party.</font>

43:52.720 --> 43:56.320
That is encouraging news.
But quite academic.

43:56.360 --> 44:00.280
As you see, I am far too busy to die.

44:00.320 --> 44:01.640
(PEEL LAUGHS)

44:12.320 --> 44:14.320
(CHUCKLES)

44:55.400 --> 44:59.200
Cotton. Whereabouts is cotton mostly?

45:01.760 --> 45:03.160
<font color="#ffff00">Manchester.</font>

45:03.200 --> 45:06.960
Yes. Rather more your sort of thing
than mine.

45:08.040 --> 45:09.960
Most of this contains industry.

46:14.560 --> 46:16.400
I'm so bored of this.

46:16.440 --> 46:21.080
<font color="#ffff00">Surely you cannot believe a senior</font>
<font color="#ffff00">member of the British Royal family</font>

46:21.120 --> 46:22.680
<font color="#ffff00">would contemplate regicide?</font>

46:22.720 --> 46:25.240
<font color="#00ff00">ERNEST: A harmless flirtation</font>
<font color="#00ff00">is what you called it.</font>

46:25.280 --> 46:27.960
<font color="#00ffff">ELIZA: You have your freedom.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Don't give it up for a man.</font>

46:28.000 --> 46:31.320
Am I simply a vessel to be protected
because I am carrying
precious cargo?

46:31.880 --> 46:33.040
(GUNSHOT)

46:33.080 --> 46:35.160
It's my duty to show myself
to my people.

46:35.200 --> 46:37.000
<font color="#ffff00">ALBERT: It's too dangerous.</font>

46:37.040 --> 46:39.440
It's starting. Albert!

